The paper discusses the use of GPUs and cloud computing for machine learning and big data applications, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the use of programming models and frameworks for cloud-native applications, which is related to Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed Systems). The use of AI techniques like machine learning and deep learning also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of scheduling policies and frameworks for effective resource management, which is related to Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
